"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:11:32.000Z","msg":"水泡係指入學要求低<br />\n<br />\n但講真係冇興趣送個工程學位比你你會讀咩?<br />\n<br />\n同埋先決條件要讀左M1M2先  又難讀<br />\n<br />\n中學已經好多人放棄數學<br />\n<br />\n畢到業果D邊係水泡D舊同學個個幾皮<br />\n<br />\n連最柒果D都2萬"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"所以DSE maths係應該分返開2個stream<br />\nStream A內容等同Core+M1<br />\nStream B內容等同Core+M2"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"玩死d文科人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T20:14:15.000Z","msg":"呢個時代冇乜可能唔讀calculus，除非上到去疊埋心水讀arts &amp; design/humanities<br />\n以前有開m&amp;s專比文商人讀，我諗m1既原意應該係dse版m&amp;s"},{"pid":"6fa24bc9cee99cdef3213fd454f4ea2917065e50","tid":2254880,"uid":370897,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T20:37:38.000Z","msg":"連登仔同高登仔好多都冇出過外國<br />\n網上人哋講咩就信咩<br />\n<br />\n見到外國乜撚野stem就出晒水<br />\n係到鳩吹外國stem啊science啊engine啊math啊係神科<br />\n現實就係non cs stem基本上係外國唔係神科<br />\n其中一部分甚至係狗也不屌<br />\n<br />\n拎美國做例子<br />\n1. college of arts and science基本上arts, social science, science任你major<br />\n你入到既話鍾意major english history定math隨便你<br />\n大家一樣major任揀,science只有神校而冇神科<br />\n<br />\n夾硬要講嘅話反而econ或者cs係神科<br />\n因為呢兩個係部分大學arts and science入面有quota,要夠分先可以declare<br />\n而且intro to econ可以開n個section個個section接近100條友<br />\n睇下你phy chem bio有冇咁多人take<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 除咗極少數神校engine係強項之外其他神校engine college係收得低過arts and science<br />\nengine神校除咗stanford berkeley mit caltech cornell cmu umich其他engine college都收得低過arts and science,有d直情好似penn比人笑engine係後門<br />\n<br />\nHarvard yale columbia chicago northwestern penn duke dartmouth brown呢堆engine都易入過正常科<br />\n<br />\n3. 有bba既學校唔少bba收得高過engine,即使係engine神校<br />\n<br />\nberkeley haas要year 3先讀得,大把人讀緊engine又好乜差都好都爭崩頭,cc轉haas難過engine<br />\numich都係<br />\ncornell aem難入過engine<br />\n<br />\n至於非engine神校個gap仲大<br />\nnyu stern, penn wharton呢啲屌打同一個學校既engine<br />\n<br />\n拎英國做例子唔寫太多<br />\n1. 牛強項唔係engine,係law ppe e&amp;m<br />\n2. 劍強項係engine,但econ呢啲更多人報<br />\n而且劍太多神科有econ law medic math<br />\n英國工程師人工低過做金融,以前比人笑嘅land econ今日仲搶手過engine<br />\n<br />\n做英國ibd個堆鬼仔拎完讀econ or land econ<br />\nhea d又職業導向<br />\n想做s&amp;t或者quant會揀math/cs<br />\nengine同nat sci唔係入唔到<br />\n只不過講hea唔夠econ hea,講學返工用到嘅coding又唔夠cs同math黎<br />\n<br />\n做ibank睇你學校同intern,有business school個堆會睇你係咪business,冇個堆wfc你讀咩科<br />\n人地hea住econ first hon你慢慢做lab做同頂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd022c729a56fe02c0446c3a0e74d1fe29bc50b","tid":2254880,"uid":186264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T22:25:46.000Z","msg":"點解呢類型既topic可以無限討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42ccaf4dd88f2e5bfb0d0b72e057e0724b9c535","tid":2254880,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fa24bc9cee99cdef3213fd454f4ea2917065e50","tid":2254880,"uid":370897,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T20:37:38.000Z","msg":"連登仔同高登仔好多都冇出過外國<br />\n網上人哋講咩就信咩<br />\n<br />\n見到外國乜撚野stem就出晒水<br />\n係到鳩吹外國stem啊science啊engine啊math啊係神科<br />\n現實就係non cs stem基本上係外國唔係神科<br />\n其中一部分甚至係狗也不屌<br />\n<br />\n拎美國做例子<br />\n1. college of arts and science基本上arts, social science, science任你major<br />\n你入到既話鍾意major english history定math隨便你<br />\n大家一樣major任揀,science只有神校而冇神科<br />\n<br />\n夾硬要講嘅話反而econ或者cs係神科<br />\n因為呢兩個係部分大學arts and science入面有quota,要夠分先可以declare<br />\n而且intro to econ可以開n個section個個section接近100條友<br />\n睇下你phy chem bio有冇咁多人take<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 除咗極少數神校engine係強項之外其他神校engine college係收得低過arts and science<br />\nengine神校除咗stanford berkeley mit caltech cornell cmu umich其他engine college都收得低過arts and science,有d直情好似penn比人笑engine係後門<br />\n<br />\nHarvard yale columbia chicago northwestern penn duke dartmouth brown呢堆engine都易入過正常科<br />\n<br />\n3. 有bba既學校唔少bba收得高過engine,即使係engine神校<br />\n<br />\nberkeley haas要year 3先讀得,大把人讀緊engine又好乜差都好都爭崩頭,cc轉haas難過engine<br />\numich都係<br />\ncornell aem難入過engine